(n = 1)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DF56EA31FF32FF6BFF43F8CE8EFAF8EC" blockId="135.[151,1436,1557,1823]" box="[199,1429,1797,1823]" pageId="135" pageNumber="136">
A detailed description is provided by 
<bibRefCitation id="BB7897C0FF32FF6BFD04F8CE88E2F8EC" author="Sasa, M. &amp; Ogata, T." box="[640,909,1797,1823]" pageId="135" pageNumber="136" pagination="85 - 104" refId="ref93427" refString="Sasa, M. &amp; Ogata, T. (1999) Taxonomic studies on the chironomid midges collected from the Kurobe Municipal Sewage Treatment Plant. Medical Entomology and Zoology, 50, 85 - 104." type="journal article" year="1999">Sasa and Ogata (1999)</bibRefCitation>
, but the wing membrane lacks macrotrichia.
</paragraph>
